<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Heaven Sweets cautions it in talks.</title>
<headline>Heaven Sweets cautions it in talks.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-09-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sweets from Heaven Ltd said on Friday it was in talks which could have an impact on its share price and urged shareholders to exercise caution in their dealings.</p>
<p>It gave no further details in a brief announcement.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
